				What can I do if the user does not have access to the website?
			  </a>
			</h3>
		  </div>
		  <div id="collapse2_0" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading0">
			<div class="panel-body px-3 mb-4">
			  <p>If the user was previously on the pre-approved list before they claimed an account, they should be instantly have access when they do claim their account.
			  If not, check in the Account Requests page to see if the user is in the list, waiting for approval. </p>
			</div>
		  </div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="panel panel-default">
		  <div class="panel-heading p-3 mb-3" role="tab" id="heading1">
			<h3 class="panel-title">
			  <a class="collapsed" role="button" title="" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2_1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse2_1">
				What can I do if I'm having trouble adding new committees?
			  </a>
			</h3>
		  </div>
		  <div id="collapse2_1" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading1">
			<div class="panel-body px-3 mb-4">
			  <p>Admins should be able to just add a name and click on the add button to create a new committee, on the set committee page. If this isn't 
			  working ensure that there isn't another committee with the same name. 
			  </p>
			</div>
		  </div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="panel panel-default">
		  <div class="panel-heading p-3 mb-3" role="tab" id="heading2">
			<h3 class="panel-title">
			  <a class="collapsed" role="button" title="" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2_2" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse2_2">
				What can I do if users have inappropriate content on their profile?
			  </a>
			</h3>
		  </div>
		  <div id="collapse2_2" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading2">
			<div class="panel-body px-3 mb-4">
			  <p>Admins have full access to all members' profiles. Admin can go the active users page and the view the member's profile 
			  and edit any inappropriate content. If the issue continues and the member becomes a malicious user, the admins have the privilege 
			  to delete the user's account, so they don't have access to the website any more. </p>
			</div>
		  </div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="panel panel-default">
		  <div class="panel-heading p-3 mb-3" role="tab" id="heading3">
			<h3 class="panel-title">
			  <a class="collapsed" role="button" title="" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2_3" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse2_3">
